        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "### After a pipeline alert\n\n1. Note the alert **start time** in Grafana (**Alerting → Alert history**).\n2. Check host log files for that window: `apps/java/logs/demo-app.json.log`, `apps/python/logs/demo-app.json.log`, `apps/rust/logs/demo-app.json.log`, `apps/react-node/logs/demo-app.json.log`, `apps/zig/logs/demo-app.json.log`, `apps/postgres/logs/postgresql-*`.\n3. In **Kibana Discover** (`logstash-*`), look for a flat gap in the chart above — lines on disk but missing in ES were not shipped.\n4. Logs: `podman compose -f docker-compose.observability.yml logs filebeat logstash --tail 100`.",
